 And so going back to the

00:03:33.130 --> 00:03:36.260
 identity one, is this the idea

00:03:36.260 --> 00:03:39.280
 that every action you take or

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:40.900
 every habit you develop is a

00:03:40.900 --> 00:03:42.640
 vote for the person you want to

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:43.320
 become?

