 It's really not unless you

00:10:58.950 --> 00:11:00.390
 stick with that habit for three

00:11:00.390 --> 00:11:01.600
 months or six months or a

00:11:01.600 --> 00:11:03.620
 year that you actually start to

00:11:03.620 --> 00:11:05.640
 see the changes you were hoping

00:11:05.640 --> 00:11:07.400
 to get when you set out.

00:11:07.400 --> 00:11:09.630
 There's this valley of death in

00:11:09.630 --> 00:11:11.780
 the beginning where in a way it

00:11:11.780 --> 00:11:13.760
 gets harder before it gets

00:11:13.760 --> 00:11:14.760
 easier.

00:11:14.760 --> 00:11:15.960
 It feels uncomfortable.

00:11:15.960 --> 00:11:17.880
 You feel sore and pain.

00:11:17.880 --> 00:11:19.250
 You feel uncertain when you

00:11:19.250 --> 00:11:20.160
 walk in the gym.

00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:21.440
 You feel like people are

00:11:21.440 --> 00:11:22.080
 judging you.

00:11:22.080 --> 00:11:23.190
 Same way with starting a

00:11:23.190 --> 00:11:23.840
 business.

00:11:23.840 --> 00:11:25.040
 In a weird way, it's harder

00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:26.240
 before it gets easier.

00:11:26.240 --> 00:11:27.570
 You start out, but you're not

00:11:27.570 --> 00:11:28.520
 making any money.

00:11:28.520 --> 00:11:29.850
 You feel stupid a lot of the

00:11:29.850 --> 00:11:31.420
 time because you don't know how

00:11:31.420 --> 00:11:32.600
 to make a sales call or

00:11:32.600 --> 00:11:34.360
 what customers are looking for

00:11:34.360 --> 00:11:36.180
 or whether you're even offering

00:11:36.180 --> 00:11:37.480
 the right product.

00:11:37.480 --> 00:11:39.240
 I remember when I first started

00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:40.830
, like I said, I didn't know

00:11:40.830 --> 00:11:41.640
 anybody.

00:11:41.640 --> 00:11:42.840
 Didn't have any entrepreneurs

00:11:42.840 --> 00:11:43.480
 in my family.

00:11:43.480 --> 00:11:44.550
 I was like, "Well, I need to

00:11:44.550 --> 00:11:45.680
 get to know some people."

00:11:45.680 --> 00:11:46.910
 I sent a bunch of emails to

00:11:46.910 --> 00:11:48.130
 reach out and just ask if

00:11:48.130 --> 00:11:49.640
 people would chat on Skype for

00:11:49.640 --> 00:11:51.720
 like 30 minutes or whatever.

00:11:51.720 --> 00:11:53.220
 I remember sending those first

00:11:53.220 --> 00:11:54.650
 few and thinking, "Do people

00:11:54.650 --> 00:11:55.480
 even do this?

00:11:55.480 --> 00:11:56.600
 Do people chat on Skype with

00:11:56.600 --> 00:11:57.710
 people that they haven't met

00:11:57.710 --> 00:11:58.200
 before?

00:11:58.200 --> 00:12:00.000
 Is this a weird thing to ask?"

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:01.890
 There's just a lot of that

00:12:01.890 --> 00:12:03.800
 uncertainty early on.

00:12:03.800 --> 00:12:05.020
 Your point is, I think, a valid

00:12:05.020 --> 00:12:06.240
 one, which is, "Well, what do

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:08.240
 you do to get through that?

00:12:08.240 --> 00:12:09.570
 How do you get through that

00:12:09.570 --> 00:12:10.880
 valley of death while you're

00:12:10.880 --> 00:12:12.140
 waiting for the long-term

00:12:12.140 --> 00:12:12.680
 rewards

00:12:12.680 --> 00:12:13.680
 to accumulate?"

00:12:13.680 --> 00:12:15.650
 I think that this is where

00:12:15.650 --> 00:12:17.430
 psychologists call it

00:12:17.430 --> 00:12:19.790
 reinforcement or an external

00:12:19.790 --> 00:12:21.040
 reinforcer,

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:22.510
 that you want some kind of

00:12:22.510 --> 00:12:24.490
 reinforcement that is enjoyable

00:12:24.490 --> 00:12:26.240
 in the moment so that you have

00:12:26.240 --> 00:12:28.720
 a reason to keep showing up.

00:12:28.720 --> 00:12:30.220
 There are from a habit

00:12:30.220 --> 00:12:32.470
 standpoint, there are two ways

00:12:32.470 --> 00:12:33.440
 to do this.

00:12:33.440 --> 00:12:35.420
 First thing is just a strategic

00:12:35.420 --> 00:12:37.410
 choice about what type of habit

00:12:37.410 --> 00:12:39.040
 you choose to follow.

00:12:39.040 --> 00:12:40.470
 If we go back to the exercise

00:12:40.470 --> 00:12:42.180
 example, well, not everybody

00:12:42.180 --> 00:12:43.640
 has to work out like a body

00:12:43.640 --> 00:12:44.640
 builder.

00:12:44.640 --> 00:12:47.190
 You could do Pilates or yoga or

00:12:47.190 --> 00:12:49.540
 go for a run or rock climbing

00:12:49.540 --> 00:12:52.280
 or all kinds of stuff.

00:12:52.280 --> 00:12:54.000
 Pick the form of a habit that

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:55.860
 brings you the most joy, that

00:12:55.860 --> 00:12:57.680
 is most enjoyable to you.

00:12:57.680 --> 00:12:58.970
 It's going to be a slog for,

00:12:58.970 --> 00:13:00.280
 you're going to have to swim

00:13:00.280 --> 00:13:01.600
 for months to see a change

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:02.600
 in your body.

00:13:02.600 --> 00:13:03.230
 You're going to have to cycle

00:13:03.230 --> 00:13:03.600
 for months.

00:13:03.600 --> 00:13:04.450
 You're going to have to lift

00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:05.200
 weights for months.

00:13:05.200 --> 00:13:06.210
 It doesn't really matter which

00:13:06.210 --> 00:13:06.840
 one you choose.

00:13:06.840 --> 00:13:08.560
 It's going to take a while.

00:13:08.560 --> 00:13:10.270
 You might as well choose the

00:13:10.270 --> 00:13:11.990
 one that's most exciting or

00:13:11.990 --> 00:13:13.320
 enjoyable to you.

00:13:13.320 --> 00:13:14.990
 Same way with like, imagine a

00:13:14.990 --> 00:13:16.080
 reading habit.

00:13:16.080 --> 00:13:17.080
 You don't have to read.

00:13:17.080 --> 00:13:18.220
 You might feel like, "Oh, I

00:13:18.220 --> 00:13:19.340
 have a business, so I need to

00:13:19.340 --> 00:13:20.520
 read business books."

00:13:20.520 --> 00:13:21.780
 But really ultimately, the most

00:13:21.780 --> 00:13:22.920
 important thing is do you get

00:13:22.920 --> 00:13:23.960
 in the habit of reading?

00:13:23.960 --> 00:13:25.610
 Do you fall in love with

00:13:25.610 --> 00:13:26.520
 reading?

00:13:26.520 --> 00:13:28.070
 If you need to start with sci-

00:13:28.070 --> 00:13:29.840
fi books or fantasy or something

00:13:29.840 --> 00:13:31.280
 like that, well, start

00:13:31.280 --> 00:13:32.280
 with that.

00:13:32.280 --> 00:13:33.990
 Do the one that is intrins

00:13:33.990 --> 00:13:36.440
ically valuable to you at first.

00:13:36.440 --> 00:13:38.230
 Once the habit is built, then

00:13:38.230 --> 00:13:39.940
 you can transition to some of

00:13:39.940 --> 00:13:41.160
 the other stuff.

00:13:41.160 --> 00:13:42.660
 That's one method for getting

00:13:42.660 --> 00:13:44.320
 through that valley of death.

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:45.320
 Yeah.

00:13:45.320 --> 00:13:48.870
 I think this brings up maybe a

00:13:48.870 --> 00:13:53.450
 harder question, which is, so

00:13:53.450 --> 00:13:56.310
 based on your book, it's

