 this month.

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:18.120
 It's great.

00:14:18.120 --> 00:14:21.620
 I was surprised by how fast I

00:14:21.620 --> 00:14:22.320
 felt.

00:14:22.320 --> 00:14:23.390
 The first day, I felt like I

00:14:23.390 --> 00:14:24.160
 didn't belong.

00:14:24.160 --> 00:14:25.160
 I felt awkward.

00:14:25.160 --> 00:14:27.130
 I don't know anybody here I'm

00:14:27.130 --> 00:14:28.160
 walking in.

00:14:28.160 --> 00:14:29.570
 Some of the machinery, I

00:14:29.570 --> 00:14:30.440
 recognize.

00:14:30.440 --> 00:14:31.440
 Some I don't.

